      "summary": "The redirect case declares two expected files, but all failed contracts can be repaired through RedirectPolicy.derive in lib/redirect_request.dart alone.",
      "evidence": [
        "RedirectPolicy.derive receives current, statusCode, and target, including the current URI, method, headers, and body, and returns the complete RedirectRequest for the next hop.",
